1. *Napada* se njegov zaštitnik. (He is attacking his defender.)
2. Oni *napadaju* protivnika u komšiluku. (They are attacking the adversary in the neighborhood.)
3. On se *napadao* sa svim snagama. (He was attacking with all his might.)
4. Oni su *napadali* svoje protivnike. (They were attacking their adversaries.)
5. Oni su *napadnuti* iznenada. (They were attacked suddenly.)
6. Oni su *napali* grad. (They attacked the city.)